  Description: "Trigger While you have your shield raised, you would take physical
    damage (bludgeoning, piercing, or slashing) from an attack.\r\nYou snap your
    shield in place to ward off a blow. Your shield prevents you from taking an amount
    of damage up to the shield\u2019s Hardness. You and the shield each take any
    remaining damage, possibly breaking or destroying the shield."
